{"tid":274783,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［住宿］去長崎別府住咩好","createTime":"2017-06-07T14:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T15:12:44.000Z","uid":2885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc0d0fd2631f67b00c78ca2714e3fac55e373e60","tid":274783,"uid":2885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:27:15.000Z","msg":"事關我8月中屋企人去福岡<br />\n<br />\n第一日就係天神住一晚酒店<br />\n<br />\n第二日就諗住落長崎玩到夜晚<br />\n<br />\n第三日就去豪斯登堡玩到夜晚係佐世保住<br />\n<br />\n第四日就搭jr去別府玩<br />\n<br />\n但係仲未搵到佐世保 別府同 長崎住宿地方 因為我加屋企人總共有8個大人4個細路 所以好多民宿都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望咁多位熟日本嘅巴絲幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a64787999a7f4dd993a0e7a1097f5f47d1cad9","tid":274783,"uid":2885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:27:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4a3aa6f7ae2dd7cebacfa91f0ea2d71146688d","tid":274783,"uid":2885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3b63573e211c0f423eaacefef3ecf32037bb0a","tid":274783,"uid":2885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"472e76527d84d3089ed9cf671c7cc04c34b6f962","tid":274783,"uid":2885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:29:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01b7dfcd0462d2de492e4ff75f510edd8c7f3174","tid":274783,"uid":2885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img sr